                  <a class="tool" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/how-to-improve-crs-score"><div class="tool-icon">UP</div><strong>Improve CRS</strong><span>10 strategies</span></a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <p class="tiny muted" style="margin-top:16px;">Disclaimer: CRS points shown are based on the official <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/express-entry/eligibility/criteria-comprehensive-ranking-system/grid.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IRCC CRS Grid</a>. The interactive checker provides estimates only — actual CRS scores are calculated by IRCC using your full Express Entry profile. Consult a <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigration-citizenship-representative/find-consultant-lawyer.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Regulated Canadian Immigration Consultant (RCIC)</a> before making immigration decisions.</p>

          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

